1. Create python3.4 virtual environment

virtualenv --no-site-packages -p /usr/bin/python3.4 ~/venv_hanabira

2. Activate virtual environment

source ~/venv_hanabira/bin/activate

3. Install requirements

./requirements.sh

4. Make config file.

cp confs/development.ini.template confs/development.ini

Edit confs/development.ini with appropriate settings

5. Create database tables

6. Run hanabira

python ./serve.py confs/development.ini
